174
00:31:08,259 --> 00:31:13,259
[SPEAKER_00] I za taj film čekamo zapravo financiranje od Havca.

175
00:31:13,259 --> 00:31:18,259
[SPEAKER_00] I jako se veselim zapravo raditi taj film.

176
00:31:18,259 --> 00:31:28,259
