184
00:31:58,259 --> 00:32:02,259
[SPEAKER_00] Uglavnom ovoga, osim toga imam puno još interesa.

185
00:32:02,259 --> 00:32:09,259
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, teško je sad sve interese reći s čim se baviš što radiš jer volim pisat.

186
00:32:09,259 --> 00:32:13,259
